{"tid":2097234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[初選一定要投票] 35+已經冇用，但係選出黎既人可能救到香港","createTime":"2020-07-06T15:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:48:11.000Z","uid":154486,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12b51c6326069aa38510ca9719d66dca22ba490c","tid":2097234,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"重點唔係果個已經廢左既立法會<br />\n係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>選左出黎既人同埋佢背後所代表既民意</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以初選時既民意back up, 就算到時香港正式鎖港封網，只要有初選獲勝既既議員成功走出國際<br />\n佢地可以幫香港人做好多事<br />\n<br />\n因為係國際眼中<br />\n佢地就係香港Pro-Democracy既代表<br />\n之後無論佢地做乜野都會增大我地既牙力<br />\n<br />\n例如成立外國流亡議會，代香港人發聲，或者做lobbying<br />\n所以初選之後出黎既人<br />\n即使比人DQ，即使立法會收皮<br />\n我地都可以壯大國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a8147e4b89e2df5ec8d7a319c040c62409acc9","tid":2097234,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbe7aa0a2cfb83ba5867fa828ad4307ba63ab6c","tid":2097234,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"販民贏左，只會一味係國安法下玩35+<br />\n<br />\n但係本土派贏左，我地國際戰線壯大既機率就越大，更多本土派手足有能力係國際線突圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2011b2d1583adf0943aed24e637573ad23f271","tid":2097234,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來初選可以咁樣玩<br />\n咁就真係唔同曬<br />\n要打議會同國際線既都一定要去投票"},{"pid":"519496eb70df193a8c3dec6fe02b448037416a22","tid":2097234,"uid":193869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re